- Vite, vite, faut y aller !

20
00:02:30,100 --> 00:02:31,900
Dépêchons !

21
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,600
Allez Kili !

22
00:03:21,700 --> 00:03:23,300
Allez ! Allez !

23
00:03:23,300 --> 00:03:25,800
Plus vite ! Plus vite !

24
00:03:29,000 --> 00:03:30,200
Si seulement nous pouvons ramener...

25
00:03:30,200 --> 00:03:33,000
