27
00:03:42,300 --> 00:03:43,600
Attention !

28
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,600
Allons.

29
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:51,700
Du nerf !

30
00:03:51,700 --> 00:03:54,100
Plus vite ! Plus vite !

31
00:03:54,200 --> 00:03:56,200
Mon or ! Mon or !

32
00:03:56,200 --> 00:03:57,200
