33
00:03:57,200 --> 00:03:58,800
Nous devons jeter quelque chose.

34
00:03:58,800 --> 00:04:01,700
Tu dois y aller, Alfrid.

35
00:04:08,800 --> 00:04:10,500
Plus vite ! Plus vite !

36
00:05:26,100 --> 00:05:28,800
Pauvres gens.

37
00:06:49,000 --> 00:06:50,100
Père !

38
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:52,400
Papa !

39
00:06:56,500 --> 00:06:57,600
