58
00:08:13,900 --> 00:08:14,800
Papa !

59
00:08:20,400 --> 00:08:21,600
Bain !

60
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:22,900
Papa !

61
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,400
Stop, stop !

62
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:36,500
Stop !

63
00:08:44,000 --> 00:08:47,800
Qui es-tu, toi qui ose

64
