102
00:13:41,100 --> 00:13:42,800
Tauriel.

103
00:13:43,900 --> 00:13:44,700
Kili ...

104
00:13:44,700 --> 00:13:46,200
Allez.

105
00:13:46,300 --> 00:13:47,900
Nous partons.

106
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:50,300
Ce sont les votres,
