sévit ici.

192
00:20:00,600 --> 00:20:01,900
Un mal ?

193
00:20:01,900 --> 00:20:05,000
Quelle sorte de mal ?

194
00:20:06,500 --> 00:20:07,800
Fili ?

195
00:20:07,800 --> 00:20:08,600
Fili !

196
00:20:09,700 --> 00:20:11,100
Fili !

197
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:41,900
De l'or.

198
00:20:45,000 --> 00:20:47,000
Au-delà de toute mesure ...

199
00:20:49,500 --> 00:20:51,100
au-delà du chagrin ...

200
00:20:51,100 --> 00:20:53,700
et des souffrances.

201
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:02,800
Admirez ... l'immense ...

202
00:21:02,800 --> 00:21:06,900
trésor de Thrór.

203
00:21:14,300 --> 00:21:15,500
Bienvenue ...

204
00:21:15,500 --> 00:21:18,300
mes chers neveux ...

205
00:21:22,100 --> 00:21:24,500
dans le Royaume ...

206
00:21:24,600 --> 00:21:26,600
d'Erebor.

207
00:21:29,500 --> 00:21:31,200
Balin !

208
00:21:33,100 --> 00:21:34,600
Bofur !

209
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:36,300
Kili !
 Bifur !

210
00:21:40,300 --> 00:21:43,800
Bombur !
- Vous êtes vivants !

211
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:47,500
Toujours aucune trace ?
- Toujours rien.

212
00:21:47,600 --> 00:21:49,800
Rien ici.
- Cherchez encore !

213
00:21:49,800 --> 00:21:51,400
Cette pierre peut être ...

214
00:21:51,500 --> 00:21:54,000
n'importe où.
- L'Arkenstone est dans cette salle.

215
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:56,400
Trouvez-là !
- Vous avez entendu, cherchez.

216
00:21:56,500 --> 00:21:58,600
Vous tous !

217
00:21:58,700 --> 00:22:00,100
Pas de repos avant de l'avoir ...

218
00:22:00,100 --> 00:22:02,300
trouver !

219
00:22:31,800 --> 00:22:36,100
<i>Je suis presque tenté de
te laisser la prendre,</i>

220
00:22:36,200 --> 00:22:37,800
<i>rien que ...</i>

221
00:22:37,800 --> 00:22:39,800
