225
00:22:45,200 --> 00:22:47,100
<i>La voir lui assécher ...</i>

226
00:22:47,100 --> 00:22:49,300
<i>le coeur ...</i>

227
00:22:49,400 --> 00:22:51,900
et le conduire à la folie.

228
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:27,500
Prenez le strict nécessaire,

229
00:23:27,500 --> 00:23:33,500
